WEBVTT

00:00:00.548 --> 00:00:02.063
Track 01.10

00:00:03.938 --> 00:00:04.318
Narrator: 1

00:00:05.288 --> 00:00:07.034
Their house is enormous!

00:00:07.426 --> 00:00:09.283
It’s got 12 bedrooms.

00:00:11.270 --> 00:00:11.690
Narrator: 2

00:00:12.716 --> 00:00:13.589
Was it hot?

00:00:13.941 --> 00:00:14.758
Yes,

00:00:14.830 --> 00:00:16.711
it was absolutely boiling!

00:00:18.722 --> 00:00:19.270
Narrator: 3

00:00:20.240 --> 00:00:20.902
Why do you look

00:00:20.942 --> 00:00:22.006
so miserable?

00:00:22.528 --> 00:00:24.870
I’ve never seen you looking so sad.

00:00:27.486 --> 00:00:28.049
Narrator: 4

00:00:29.043 --> 00:00:30.670
We had a brilliant holiday.

00:00:31.347 --> 00:00:32.196
The hotel,

00:00:32.435 --> 00:00:32.991
the weather,

00:00:33.174 --> 00:00:33.881
the town –

00:00:34.390 --> 00:00:35.898
it was all really good.

00:00:38.569 --> 00:00:39.196
Narrator: 5

00:00:40.215 --> 00:00:41.044
The food was

00:00:41.100 --> 00:00:42.711
absolutely awful.

00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:44.780
I’m not going there again!

00:00:47.379 --> 00:00:48.022
Narrator: 6

00:00:48.995 --> 00:00:50.487
I was furious when I

00:00:50.558 --> 00:00:52.875
found out he’d read my private diary!

00:00:55.508 --> 00:00:56.024
Narrator: 7

00:00:57.065 --> 00:00:58.454
The picture’s tiny –

00:00:58.970 --> 00:01:00.042
I can’t see it.

00:01:00.928 --> 00:01:02.404
Can you make it a bit bigger?

00:01:05.026 --> 00:01:05.510
Narrator: 8

00:01:06.464 --> 00:01:07.623
It’s freezing!

00:01:08.100 --> 00:01:09.846
Why didn’t I bring a coat?

00:01:10.508 --> 00:01:10.897
Here,

00:01:11.191 --> 00:01:12.683
you can borrow my jacket.

00:01:15.370 --> 00:01:15.918
Narrator: 9

00:01:16.911 --> 00:01:18.721
Your T-shirt’s filthy!

00:01:19.422 --> 00:01:20.945
Put it in the washing machine.

00:01:23.602 --> 00:01:24.054
Narrator: 10

00:01:25.087 --> 00:01:26.698
That cake is delicious!

00:01:27.558 --> 00:01:29.129
Could I have some more, please?